            "name": "Description",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "The leaders of small orc warbands aren\u2019t much smarter or more cunning than the rank-and-file orc warriors they lead\u2014but just a small advantage in strength is enough to let them take the best shares of treasure and slaves and lord their dominance over their fellow orcs. Orc commanders enforce discipline through intimidation and are not afraid to lead underlings to their deaths."
